  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read existing `SendEmailDialog/SendEmailDialog.tsx` to inventory the legacy public API (`onSend` callback, etc.) — document in task notes for Wave 3 consumer migration reference.</step>
    <step order="2">Author canonical `EmailComposer/wrappers/SendEmailDialog.tsx`:
      - `ISendEmailDialogProps` per prompt
      - `forwardRef` not required — wrapper drives the engine internally (consumers don't need imperative access)
      - Use internal `composerRef = useRef&lt;IEmailComposerHandle&gt;(null)` to call `send()` after own validation flow
      - Default `attachmentSources` to `[{ kind: 'local' }, { kind: 'spe' }]` if not provided
      - On engine's send-success callback → `onSent(communicationId)` then `onClose()`
      - On engine's send-error callback → `onError(err)` (no auto-close)
      - Render `&lt;Dialog open={open}...&gt;&lt;DialogSurface&gt;&lt;DialogBody&gt;&lt;EmailComposer mount='dialog' ref={composerRef} ... /&gt;&lt;/DialogBody&gt;&lt;/DialogSurface&gt;&lt;/Dialog&gt;`</step>
    <step order="3">Rewrite `SendEmailDialog/SendEmailDialog.tsx` to a one-liner re-export:
      <code>
      export { SendEmailDialog } from '../EmailComposer/wrappers/SendEmailDialog';
      export type { ISendEmailDialogProps } from '../EmailComposer/wrappers/SendEmailDialog';
      </code>
      Remove all legacy implementation code from this file.</step>
    <step order="4">Update `SendEmailDialog/index.ts` to export from the re-export above.</step>
    <step order="5">Update `EmailComposer/index.ts` — export `SendEmailDialog`, `ISendEmailDialogProps`.</step>
    <step order="6">Run `npm run build` — verify legacy import path still resolves; grep for `import.*SendEmailDialog` across repo to confirm no broken paths.</step>
    <step order="7">Run `npm run lint` clean.</step>
    <step order="7.5">Step 9.5 quality gates — code-review + adr-check (ADR-019, ADR-021, ADR-028, ADR-033).</step>
    <step order="8">Update `TASK-INDEX.md`: 022 ✅. Add a note in PR description: "Legacy `onSend` callback removed; Wave 3 task 051 migrates FilePreviewDialog to `onSent`/`onError`."</step>
    <step order="9">Update `current-task.md` per task-execute protocol.</step>
  </steps>

