  <notes>
    Per CLAUDE.md Empirical Finding: only `LegalWorkspace/.../FilePreviewDialog.tsx` known to consume `SendEmailDialog`. Grep at Wave 3 start confirms whether any other consumer exists. The grep step here is purely a guard against silent breakage.

    Legacy `onSend` callback removal IS a breaking change for the LegalWorkspace consumer. Wave 3 task 051 fixes it in the same merge window. Until task 051 lands, LegalWorkspace's `FilePreviewDialog.tsx` will have a TypeScript error — acceptable for the wave-internal transition window.
